 P(\exists\, n\in\mathbb{N}: X_n\neq Y_n)=P\Big(\bigcup_n \,[X_n\neq Y_n]\Big)\leq \sum_nP(X_n\neq Y_n)=0 
 P(X_n=Y_n,\,\forall n\in\mathbb{N})=1-P(\exists\, n\in\mathbb{N}: X_n\neq Y_n)=1. 
